definitions.definition: possibly, probably; as I was told (modal particle expressing an assumption, often like English must + infinitive, or  guess + clause)

parsedExamples.example: Er ist wohl schon gegangen.He must have left already.
parsedExamples.translation: I guess he has left already.

parsedExamples.example: Seine Frau ist wohl irgendeine bekannte Ärztin.
parsedExamples.translation: [I heard that] his wife is some well-known doctor.
